&lt;h1 class=&quot;smallTitle positionSubTitle brandColoredText&quot;&gt;DESCRIPTION&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;userDesignedContent company-description&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a thoughtful, resourceful, and customer-centric Customer Support Representative to join our NYC-based team. This role is ideal for someone who thrives in problem solving, communicates with clarity and empathy, and is comfortable navigating ambiguity to find the right answer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a CSR at Pontera, you’ll serve as a trusted partner to our clients — guiding them through questions, troubleshooting issues, and ensuring they feel heard, supported, and confident in our platform. You won’t always have an immediate answer — but you’ll know how to investigate, collaborate, and follow through until you do.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an opportunity to make a meaningful impact within a growing and evolving company where operational excellence and customer experience are central to our success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
