&lt;li&gt;Respond to client questions in a clear, thorough, and timely manner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Investigate issues and determine next steps when solutions are not immediately obvious&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Escalate complex technical matters to appropriate internal teams, providing full context and documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate and solve issues with customers and cross functional teams by phone, email, video chat&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify patterns or recurring themes clients are experiencing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support team initiatives and projects that enhance the customer experience&lt;/li&gt;
